<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-37-0445 </DOCNO><TEXT>Berty Reaction Engineers, Ltd. (BREL) is developing two new laboratoryrecycle reactors, the ROTOBERTY and the TURBOBERTY. These new reactorsare basically improved versions of the original Berty reactor. To understandwhy the reactors have the features that they do, it is first necessaryto briefly review laboratory reactors in general and specifically theoriginal Berty reactor.</TEXT></DOC>